    "name": "PIREND7",
    "steam_appid": 3176460,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好进入Pirend7的肾上腺素世界，在这里，高速竞速与爆炸性战斗在32人对战中碰撞。在这款科幻竞速游戏中，生存不仅仅依赖速度；更依赖策略、火力和技巧。不论你是冲向终点线，还是奋战到最后一人，每场比赛都是对智慧、反应能力和战斗能力的考验。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>释放PIREND的力量</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176460/extras/d8b2186f3684e56255cbdf32f822e41e.poster.avif?t=1748300161\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176460/extras/d8b2186f3684e56255cbdf32f822e41e.webm?t=1748300161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176460/extras/d8b2186f3684e56255cbdf32f822e41e.mp4?t=1748300161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pirend是这个舞台上的明星——它们是为速度、破坏和战略统治而设计的未来派重型武装载具。每个Pirend都属于一个独特的类别，提供独特的被动、主要和终极技能，能够让你在战斗中占据优势。无论你是依靠强大的火力主宰战场，还是通过战略精确击败对手，你的类别和技能选择将定义你取得胜利的方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>多样化的武器库</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176460/extras/6daeeac0a861b2f2324a1858b05746d5.poster.avif?t=1748300161\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176460/extras/6daeeac0a861b2f2324a1858b05746d5.webm?t=1748300161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176460/extras/6daeeac0a861b2f2324a1858b05746d5.mp4?t=1748300161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为你的Pirend装备超过25种武器，以适应你的战斗风格。不论你偏好精准的步枪、强力的加农炮、近距离毁灭性的霰弹枪，还是无情扫射的机枪，你的装备可以根据任何情况进行定制。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>战术小工具</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176460/extras/55716f9c875c4ebff24647bacb8bc051.poster.avif?t=1748300161\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176460/extras/55716f9c875c4ebff24647bacb8bc051.webm?t=1748300161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176460/extras/55716f9c875c4ebff24647bacb8bc051.mp4?t=1748300161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用多达三个战术小工具掌控战场。从7种独特的装备中选择，例如部署“护盾”以吸收敌方火力，释放“烟幕”甩掉追击者，或者使用“武器增强器”提升火力。小工具提供了广泛的战略选择，可以扭转任何战斗的局势，并且在游戏中可以更换小工具，迅速适应任何情况。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>先进的导弹系统</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176460/extras/51f017ca1f6ffaaef07312571f12a6e5.poster.avif?t=1748300161\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176460/extras/51f017ca1f6ffaaef07312571f12a6e5.webm?t=1748300161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176460/extras/51f017ca1f6ffaaef07312571f12a6e5.mp4?t=1748300161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个Pirend都配备了多功能导弹发射器，能够根据需要发射7种特制导弹。无论你是需要用“反装甲导弹”穿透护甲，用“反盾导弹”摧毁敌方护盾，还是用“EMP导弹”干扰电子设备，你的导弹发射器都是造成严重伤害的首选工具。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>增强系统</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176460/extras/205c3bec554abe252f2085b29df5b769.avif?t=1748300161\" width=600 height=342 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着你竞速和战斗，你将解锁随机增强，提升你的Pirend能力。拥有40种不同的增强可供选择，你可以减少小工具的冷却时间，加倍导弹发射器的火力，或者强化你的护盾，让你能够快速适应和进化你的策略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>动态赛道</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pirend7的赛道从宽敞逐渐变窄，迫使玩家进入激烈的近距离战斗。准备好为每一寸道路而战！</p>",
